candidates.stmt:
As a retired Police Detective, businessman and former council worker I’m committed to:
•	Making our city safer;
•	Providing housing for Milton Keynes citizens and our Military Veterans first;
•	Addressing antisocial behaviour;
•	Helping small businesses; and
•	Improving our current infrastructure before allowing anymore expansion. 
I will listen to residents and work hard for our community because your voice matters and deserves to be heard.

Only a vote for Reform UK will bring real change to our unique city.
